description: I just left the metro when I noticed a boy. I stopped him at the exit and asked him for a short interview. He was in a hurry but when he heard something about money he was at least willing to listen. He realized very soon what all my talk was about. He said that he was not for sale. But still - as he was broke - he agreed to sell me his undies. Not bad for a start. A few minutes later I saw the next boy. He immediately asked me for my cam. Maybe he thought that I record for the TV. When I started to offer him money for some crazy tasks he was more than willing and agreed to show me his chest and butt. Then I offered him money to compare our dicks. So we went to the bushes and well... check it out.
title: Czech Hunter 46
